transformations.description:
This SQL code defines two Common Table Expressions (CTEs): `LatestAgentData_CTE` and `LatestAccountDetail_CTE`. These CTEs fetch distinct agent data and account details where `RowEffEndDt` is '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'.

The main query then retrieves various policy details from the `int_msgr.policydetail` table. This includes direct policy attributes, several conditional translations (e.g., translating `PolicyNumber` or `ControllingStateCd` to specific values or descriptions), and defaulting certain fields to "Not Applicable" or "Other" if they are null. 

This main query does three `LEFT JOIN` operations:
1. It joins with `int_msgr.dim_insurance_score` to match insurance scores with their display values.
2. It joins with the `LatestAgentData_CTE` to get agent-related details.
3. It joins with the `LatestAccountDetail_CTE` to get account-related details
transformations.name: SQ_PolicyDetails_GW

object.customQuery:
WITH LatestAgentData_CTE AS (
   SELECT
        agentcd,
        ProducerName,
        AgencyCd,
        PaymentPreferenceCd,
        roweffstrtdt
    FROM
        int_msgr.agents
    WHERE
        RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
),
LatestAccountDetail_CTE AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT PolicyKey, BillingType,roweffstrtdt
    FROM int_msgr.accountdetail
    WHERE RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
),
LatestInsuredDetail_CTE AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM int_msgr.insureddetail
    WHERE RowEffEndDt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
),
LatestAttachmentDetails_CTE AS (
SELECT
    LEFT(PolicyKey, LENGTH(PolicyKey) - 3) AS policy_num,
    MAX(AddDt) AS latest_inspection_date
FROM
    int_msgr.attachmentdetail
WHERE
    RowEffEndDt > SYSDATE
    AND (
        TemplateId = 'MPolicyAttachment0017'
        OR (
            TemplateId = 'LegacySystemDocumentPolicy'
            AND (
                Description LIKE 'Inspections%'
                OR Description LIKE 'Inspection Report %'
                OR Description = 'Report'
                OR Description LIKE 'Report%Loc%'
            )
        )
    )
GROUP BY
    LEFT(PolicyKey, LENGTH(PolicyKey) - 3))


SELECT distinct
   'Guidewire' as datasource_name,
   P.FullPolicyKey AS policy_key,
   p.PolicyNumber AS policy_number,
   P.PolicyNumber as gw_policy_number,
     ( CASE
			WHEN P.PolicyNumber = 'FP24008446'
				THEN 'Cambridge'
			ELSE p.CarrierCd
			END
		) AS company_desc,
COALESCE(
	(
		CASE
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'CT' THEN 'CT (06)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'IL' THEN 'IL (12)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'ME' THEN 'ME (18)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'MA' THEN 'MA (20)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'NH' THEN 'NH (28)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'NJ' THEN 'NJ (29)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'NY' THEN 'NY (31)'
			WHEN P.ControllingStateCd = 'RI' THEN 'RI (38)'
			ELSE p.ControllingStateCd
		END
	), 'Not Applicable'
) AS controlling_state,
    COALESCE(P.StatusCd , 'Not Applicable') AS policy_status,
	COALESCE(P.StatusCd , 'Not Applicable') AS renewal_code_desc,
    COALESCE( p.GroupLine,'Not Applicable') AS lob_group_desc,
    COALESCE(P.NewRenewalCd ,'Not Applicable') AS new_renewal_desc,
	COALESCE(P.NewRenewalCd,'Not Applicable') AS new_renewal_indicator,
    COALESCE(
	(
		CASE
			WHEN P.PolicyNumber = 'SBP34002370'
				THEN 'Businessowners'
			ELSE p.LineOfBusiness
		END
	), 'Not Applicable'
) AS lob_desc,
    P.PolicyEffectiveDt  AS policy_effective_date,
	P.PolicyExpirationDt AS  policy_expiration_date,
	P.PolicyInceptionDt AS policy_inception_date,
    SUBSTRING(p."PolicyNumber", 1,
  CAST(
    POSITION(regexp_substr(p."PolicyNumber", '[0-9]') IN p."PolicyNumber") AS INTEGER
  ) - 1
)  AS policy_symbol
,
COALESCE(P.PolicyForm,'Not Applicable') AS form,
    P.PolicyVersion AS module_number,
	P.NewBusinessTransactionDt AS policy_transaction_dt,
    COALESCE(P.PayPlanCd,'Not Applicable') AS pay_plan,
    COALESCE(P.AutomaticRenewal,'Not Applicable') AS automatic_renewal,
    P.Operator as operator,
    P.InexperiencedOperator AS inexperienced_operator,
    P.CustomerNumber AS customer_number,
    COALESCE(P.SourceCd,'Not Applicable') AS source_cd,
    COALESCE(RIGHT(A.AgentCd, 4),'Not Applicable') AS producer_code,
    COALESCE(A.ProducerName ,'Not Applicable') AS producer_name,
	COALESCE(P.InsuranceScore,'Other') AS insurance_score,
    COALESCE(i.display_value ,'Other') AS insurance_score_desc,
	COALESCE(p.secondaryinsurancescore,'Other') AS secondary_insurance_score,
    COALESCE(si.display_value,'Other') AS secondary_insurance_score_desc,

	AcD.BillingType AS billing_type,
	'No' AS fairplan_desc,
	 A.PaymentPreferenceCd AS payment_preference,
	 p.PolicySystemID AS policy_system_id,
	 p.PolicyKey AS part_policy_key,
	 CASE
        WHEN p.isMigrated = 'Yes' AND p.LineOfBusiness IN ('Homeowners', 'Dwelling', 'Businessowners')
            THEN RIGHT(p.PolicyNumber, 7)
    END AS legacy_policy_number,
	A.AgencyCd AS agency_code,
	p.CancelReason AS cancel_reason,
    p.ProgramCd AS program,
    p.Tier AS tier,
    p.NonrenewalReasons AS nonrenewal_reasons,
	P.RiskTypeCd AS risk_type,
    P.ShellPolicyInd AS shell_policy_ind,
    P.insurancescorerundate AS insurance_score_run_date,
    P.insurancescorerunyear AS insurance_score_run_year,
    P.secondaryinsurancescorerundate AS secondary_insurance_score_run_date,
    p.secondaryinsurancescorerunyear AS secondary_insurance_score_run_year,
    ad.latest_inspection_date,
    ID.InsuredName AS insured_name,
    TRIM(BOTH ',' FROM
    COALESCE(NULLIF(ID.InsuredAddress1, '') || ',', '') ||
    COALESCE(NULLIF(ID.InsuredAddress2, '') || ',', '') ||
    COALESCE(NULLIF(ID.InsuredCity, '') || ',', '') ||
    COALESCE(NULLIF(ID.InsuredZip, ''), '')
    ) AS insured_address,
    ID.FormattedInsuredAddress AS formatted_insured_address,
	ID.InsuredBirthDt AS insured_birth_dt,
ID.InsuredZip AS insured_zip_code
FROM int_msgr.policydetail P
inner JOIN LatestInsuredDetail_CTE ID ON ID.PolicyKey = P.PolicyKey
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.dim_insurance_score i ON p.InsuranceScore::int BETWEEN i.low AND i.hi
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.dim_insurance_score si ON p.InsuranceScore::int BETWEEN si.low AND si.hi
LEFT JOIN LatestAgentData_CTE A ON P.ProviderNumber = A.AgentCd 
LEFT JOIN LatestAccountDetail_CTE AcD ON AcD.PolicyKey = p.PolicyKey
LEFT JOIN LatestAttachmentDetails_CTE ad ON P.PolicyNumber= ad.policy_num
LEFT join cert_msgr.dim_policy tg_p on tg_p.policy_key=p.fullpolicykey

transformations.description:
This query fetches policy details from the int_msgr.PMS_Master_Policy_Hist table and maps them to standardized fields.
The source of the data is denoted as 'PMS'.
Fields without direct mappings or that are not present in the source are filled with default values like 'Not Applicable', NULL, or specific data types.
The query also joins with several reference tables to retrieve descriptive values for specific fields, such as RenewalCode and Line of Business.
The result includes various policy attributes, such as policy number, company, status, line of business, effective dates, and many others.
transformations.name: SQ_master_policy_pms

object.customQuery:
WITH LatestInspection AS (
   SELECT Policy_Number as policy_number_pms
        ,CAST(MAX(Inspection_Dt) AS TIMESTAMP) AS latest_inspection_date
    FROM int_msgr.pms_inspection
    GROUP BY Policy_Number

)
SELECT distinct
    'PMS' as datasource_name,
    P.Policy_Key AS policy_key,
	p.Formatted_Policy_Number  AS policy_number,
    P.Formatted_Policy_Number AS gw_policy_number,
    P.Company_Desc AS company_desc,
COALESCE(Rs.gen4_desc, 'Not Applicable') as controlling_state,
COALESCE(rc.Display_RenewalCd , 'Not Applicable') AS policy_status,
	COALESCE(rc.Display_RenewalCd , 'Not Applicable') AS renewal_code_desc,
    COALESCE(lob.LOB_Display_Group_Desc,'Not Applicable') AS lob_group_desc,
	COALESCE(P.New_Renewal_Desc ,'Not Applicable') AS new_renewal_desc,
	COALESCE(P.New_Renewal_Desc ,'Not Applicable') AS new_renewal_indicator,
 COALESCE(lob.LOB_Display_Desc,'Not Applicable') AS lob_desc,
	P.Policy_Effective_Date  AS policy_effective_date,
    P.Policy_Expiration_Date AS  policy_expiration_date,
    P.Policy_Inception_Date::TIMESTAMP AS policy_inception_date,
    P.Policy_Symbol AS policy_symbol,
    P.Formatted_Module_Number as module_number,
COALESCE(P.Policy_Form,'Not Applicable') AS form ,
    P.New_Business_Entry_Date AS policy_transaction_dt,
    'Not Applicable' AS pay_plan,
    'Not Applicable' AS automatic_renewal,
    NULL::INT AS operator,
    NULL::INT AS inexperienced_operator,
    P.Formatted_Policy_Number AS customer_number,
    'Not Applicable' AS source_cd,
    COALESCE(P.Producer_Code,'Not Applicable') AS producer_code,
    'Not Applicable' AS producer_name,
	COALESCE(CAST(P.Insurance_Score AS VARCHAR),'Other') AS insurance_score,
    COALESCE(P.Insurance_Score_Desc ,'Other') AS insurance_score_desc,
    COALESCE(CAST(P.insurance_score_2 AS VARCHAR),'Other') AS secondary_insurance_score,
	COALESCE(P.insurance_score_desc_2 ,'Other') AS secondary_insurance_score_desc,
	P.BillingType AS billing_type,
    P.Fairplan_Desc AS fairplan_desc,
	NULL AS payment_preference,
	NULL::BIGINT AS policy_system_id,
	NULL AS part_policy_key,
	NULL AS legacy_policy_number,
	P.agency_code as agency_code,
	NULL AS cancel_reason,
	P.program AS program,
	P.tier AS tier,
	NULL AS nonrenewal_reasons,
	NULL AS risk_type,
	NULL AS shell_policy_ind,
	NULL::TIMESTAMP AS                insurance_score_run_date,
    P.insurance_score_year::smallint AS insurance_score_run_year,
    NULL::TIMESTAMP AS secondary_insurance_score_run_date,
    p.insurance_score_2_year::smallint AS secondary_insurance_score_run_year,
	ad.latest_inspection_date,
	TRIM(ID.Insured_Name) AS insured_name,
    TRIM(ID.Insured_Address1) || ',' ||
    TRIM(ID.Insured_Address2) || ',' ||
    TRIM(ID.Insured_City) || ',' ||
    TRIM(ID.Insured_Zip) AS insured_address,
   TRIM(ID.FormattedInsuredAddress) AS formatted_insured_address,
    CAST(NULL  AS TIMESTAMP) AS insured_birth_dt,
    TRIM(ID.Insured_Zip) AS insured_zip_code

	FROM int_msgr.PMS_Master_Policy_Hist P
LEFT JOIN cert_msgr.dim_policy tg_p on tg_p.policy_key=P.policy_key
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.RenewalCode_Ref rc ON rc.PMSRenewalCd = P.Policy_Renewal_Code
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.LOB_Ref lob ON lob.PMS_LOB_Desc = P.Lob_Desc
LEFT join int_msgr.HIER_dim_RiskState RS on Rs.dim_id=P.Risk_State
LEFT JOIN LatestInspection ad ON p.Policy_Number = ad.policy_number_pms
LEFT JOIN int_msgr.PMS_Master_Insured ID ON ID.Policy_Key = P.Policy_Key
where P.row_end_dt='9999-12-31'
